          <p><b>The solar home lighting system is an excellent solution for domestic lighting (DC) in
            rural/urban areas and especially in remote areas whice are inaccessible by the power
            grid. A typical solar home lighting system comprises of solar PV module, battery(LMLA/VRLA), charge controller connected in a sequence to provide power to domestic
            load (like luminaries, protable TV, redio, DC fan etc.) the battery and module ratings are
            selectable as per the load requirement. The systems are designed typically to give a
            daily working time of 3-4 hours. The system is tested as per MNRE technical
            requirements/standards.</b></p>
