          <p><b>The solar street lighting system caters to needbased street lighting and outdoor/garden
            lighting. It gives 10-12 hours of continuous, bright, cooler light, with automatic dusk to
            down controls. A typical SSLS comprises of a CFL/LED luminary light source, battery
            (LMLA/VRLA) for storage of electricity, PV module for charging the battery, charge
            controller for safe charging and discharging of battery and dusk-to-dawn controls for
            operating the lamp. The system is tested as per MNRE technical
            requirements/standards.</b></p>
