          <p><b>Primarily developed to monitor the performance of a Solar PV Power Plant (SPP)of any
            size, to maximize solar power harvesting and reduce maintenance cost and time, for
            analysis of the plant performance data. It also has the capability to transfer the logged
            data to Agni’s server for remote monitoring purpose. Generally Agni provides a user ID
            and a password to the intended customer for monitoring purpose. Customer can
            monitor their SPP remotely with the help of a monitoring web-portal, with the supplied
            ID and password, using any standard web-browser like Mozilla, firefox, google
            chrome.Agni will maintain the server, reducing the customer’s effort to maintain the
            same.</b></p></h4>
